  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Hive Imp/exp]]></title>
    <link href="http://idflai.github.io/blog/2014/01/17/hive-imp-slash-exp/"/>
    <updated>2014-01-17T13:47:11+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://idflai.github.io/blog/2014/01/17/hive-imp-slash-exp</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一、hive数据导出   <!--more-->
1.将select的结果放到一个的的表格中（首先要用create table创建新的表格）</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>insert overwrite table test
</span><span class='line'>select uid,name from test2;</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>2.将select的结果放到本地文件系统中</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>INSERT OVERWRITE LOCAL DIRECTORY '/tmp/reg_3' SELECT a.* FROM events a;</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>3.将select的结果放到hdfs文件系统中</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/hdfs_out' SELECT a.* FROM invites a WHERE 
</span><span class='line'>a.ds='&lt;DATE&gt;';</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>二、hive数据导入</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>CREATE TABLE logs(logs string);
</span><span class='line'>LOAD DATA [LOCAL] INPATH '/data/userdata' [OVERWRITE] INTO TABLE logs;</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>直接从从其它的表拖数据过来</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE TMP_T1 SELECT * FROM TMP_T2;</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
